Package: cistem
Type: Package
Title: A 'Stemmer' for German
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: c( person("Florian", "Schwendinger", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "FlorianSchwendinger@gmx.at"),
              person("Leonie", "Weissweiler", role = c("aut", "cph")) )
Description: 'CISTEM' is a stemming algorithm for the German language,
	the algorithm is available for different languages at
	<https://github.com/LeonieWeissweiler/CISTEM>. This package contains
	an interface to the 'C++' version of the code.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Imports: Rcpp (>= 0.12.17)
LinkingTo: Rcpp
